title: UPDATED: What to do w/ 11k tokens and $17k vault profits?
body:
Here is a link to all of the proposals:
https://docs.google.com/document/d/1rwjR00wKWL3p0phKCpikEdmiMUzuUHwsGIeQHAh7sTw/edit

I'll give a brief summary of each one, but please read the doc for more details.

1] tldr: burn the 10k tokens in small batches over time until the price on uni goes up. 1k tokens to Owen. Do nothing with $17k.

2] tldr: burn all 11k tokens, pay out $5k to Owen and Zebrains, and distribute $12k to mod team.

3] tldr: don’t burn the 11k tokens, pay Owen and Zebrains $8.5k apiece. Separately, collect ETH from holders to hire new devs to fork yfbeta.

4] tldr; burn 10k of tokens, put $17k into the multisig for dev, mod, and marketing expenses (tbd).

5] tldr; distribute $17k profits to all existing token holders. Do nothing with tokens.
author: 0x056590F16D5b314a132BbCFb1283fEc5D5C6E670
